start.label: when cat's away mice will play

examples.en: Did anything happen in my absence?
She returned to the company after a long absence.
He had many absences from work.
I expected to see her and was surprised by her absence.
The boy's absence from class has been noted.
Absence makes the heart grow fonder.
His very absence is eloquent.
I gave a reason for my absence.
He was surprised by the absence of any explanation.
His absence unbound his sister's tongue.
Paul was praying that no one had noticed his absence.
Who has been placed in charge during the director's absence?
Her work involved repeated absences from home.
Absence of mind is altogether an involuntary thing.
Freedom consists in the absence of oppressive laws.
After two years' absence Richard returned to England.
In the absence of consensus no decision could be reached.
Unauthorized absence is sufficient reason for dismissal.
She's been given leave of absence to attend a computer course.
His fearful family would count in agony the hours of his absence.
The President's absence has given rise to speculation about his health.
His absence is the hinge of our plan.
He criticized her routine absence from important meetings.
Occasional absence from work is not a valid reason for dismissal.
Their story explaining their absence was met with frank disbelief.
An employee on an unpaid leave of absence does not receive pay for the holiday.
My heart is laden with sorrow at the thought of your continued absence.
My absence will entail inconvenience upon you.
Her father's illness excused her absence.
The products showed a remarkable absence of defects.
